  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nSolutions\nTools\nResources\nPricing\nEN\nSign in\nRequest a demo\nStart free trial\nPerplexity Visibility Tracker\n\nSee how your brand stacks up in Perplexity answers. Use our new Perplexity brand monitoring tool to track mentions, links, competitors, and measure your impact\n\nStart free trial\nRequest a demo\n\nNo credit card required\n\nTrusted by 40,000+ agencies\n\nPerplexity Visibility Tracker\n\nTrack brand and website presence in Perplexity answers\n\nSee what Perplexity says when responding to your keywords\n\nTrack website links and monitor brand mentions in Perplexity\n\nAnalyze your brand’s rankings in Perplexity’s AI responses\n\nCheck competitors and compare visibility side by side\n\nReview historical trends and visibility changes in Perplexity\n\nStart free trial\nAnalyze how Perplexity and other AI platforms position your brand. Keep your voice strong and your reputation consistent!\nTry now\nPerplexity visibility tracking software built around your needs\n\nFill the gaps in your strategy with brand visibility insights from Perplexity AI\n\nAnalyze how Perplexity positions your brand\n\nDiscover how your business is portrayed across Perplexity answers to ensure it reflects your brand’s image, voice, and expertise.\n\nEvaluate your brand’s visibility in Perplexity\n\nMonitor how often your brand is cited and linked in Perplexity. See positions, track changes over time, measure the impact of your efforts.\n\nExplore the sources in Perplexity answers\n\nGet the list of domains and URLs Perplexity pulls into its answers. See the source type (media, blogs, forums) to understand what content Perplexity favors in your niche\n\nTrack competitor visibility alongside yours\n\nSee how you compare to the competition. Discover how often your rivals are mentioned, where you stand, and how to outperform them.\n\nGet visibility data tailored to your market\n\nTrack how Perplexity responds to your prompts across different countries and langua",
